33#define _DRM_INTEL_GTT_H_

36#include <sys/bus.h>
37
38struct pci_dev;
39struct agp_bridge_data;
40
41void intel_gtt_get(uint64_t * /* GPU VA size in bytes */,
42 size_t * /* graphics stolen memory in bytes */,
43 bus_addr_t * /* aperture base */,
44 uint64_t * /* aperture size in bytes */);
45int intel_gmch_probe(struct pci_dev *, struct pci_dev *,
46 struct agp_bridge_data *);
47void intel_gmch_remove(void);
48bool intel_enable_gtt(void);
49void intel_gtt_chipset_flush(void);
50void intel_gtt_insert_sg_entries(bus_dmamap_t, unsigned, unsigned);
51void intel_gtt_clear_range(unsigned, unsigned);
52

54#define AGP_USER_CACHED_MEMORY 2

56extern int intel_iommu_gfx_mapped;
